  * Add Line0 to Line5 to TriggerSource Enum
  * Fix: nodelet namespace
  * Fix: onInit deadlock
  * Contributors: Dominik Kleiser, Boitumelo Ruf, Thomas Emter, Peter Mortimer, tas, Geoff McIver

